author: Adam Shaw
title: Lawmakers call on WHO chief to retract pro-China comments on coronavirus
description: A resolution being introduced in both the House and the Senate is calling on the head of the World Health Organization (WHO) to retract “highly misleading” statement about the Chinese government’s  response to the coronavirus.
